trong>WordPress Authorize.Net Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> Power your travel and tour website with the our Authorize.Net WordPress plugin and offer a wide range of payment options to your online customers for booking your trip and travel packages. This WP Travel payment add-on makes collecting payments through credit cards quick and painless. It can accept international payments from anywhere in the world as long as your tour business is based in the United Kingdom, United States, Canada, Europe or Australia.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress RazorPay Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> RazorPay is a popular payment gateway in India. Install RazorPay payment gateway in seconds using our plugin and enable the ability to receive international payments in India for tour bookings from anywhere around the globe.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Stripe WordPress Plugin:<\\/strong> Stripe is one of the largest payment companies in the world which processes payments of multiple sources. Along with it also offers a secure and seamless environment for users and merchants to do online transactions. With all the coding done, you can download and install this plugin on your site in a fly!\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress Instamojo Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> Instamojo payment gateway is one of the most popular payment options used by online platforms across the world. Our Instamojo payment plugin for WordPress offers easy-to-install and easy-to-use payment options for end users and travel site owners for process credit card, debit card, net banking payments, among others.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>WordPress Khalti Payment Plugin:<\\/strong> For Nepali travel agencies, the Khalti WordPress plugin is a savior. It allows users to book and pay for their trips using the Khalti payment gateway. With multiple payment options like debit cards of various Nepali banks, Khalti wallets, and e-banking payments, this plugin accepts all the local payments in Nepali rupees for Nepali travel and tour websites.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"19.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 11475,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-partial-payment\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Partial Payment\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-03-06 10:33:50\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-12-18 07:30:55\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=11475\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-13522 size-full\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/partial_payment.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1497\\\" height=\\\"614\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nAre you looking for a WordPress booking partial payment plugin for a travel website? Then our WP Travel Partial Payment add on is the right choice for you. This is a plugin addon that works in sync with our main plugin WP Travel \\u2013 <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/\\\">the best free tour itinerary management plugin on WordPress.<\\/a> It allows your customer to pay for the trip package in installment and helps you keeping track of remaining amounts.\\r\\n\\r\\nThrough WordPress Partial Payment plugin, you can easily specify the partial payment plan of a trip while creating the package. So, the customer can book travel and tour package at specified installment cost and time. It can also be integrated with multiple payment gateways including PayPal, InstaMojo, PayStack, PayFast, Stripe, RazorPay, and Khalti (presently it does not support Authorize.Net). Providing the customer the flexibility to choose the payment gateway they prefer.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>NOTE:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>This WordPress Booking Partial Payment plugin is ONLY for Travel websites.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>This plugin works ONLY with WP Travel Plugin.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>This plugin comes integrated into the<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-travel-pro\\/\\\"> premium version of WP Travel Pro<\\/a> \\u2013 means you don\\u2019t have to purchase it standalone if you are WP Travel Pro user.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>This plugin does not a partial payment option for Authorize.Net payment gateway.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>How Does Partial Payment Help a Travel Website Generate More Business?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nMany travelers are not able to afford the full payment at once. They may be even uncertain and insecure about booking online travel and tour package. In such a situation, encouraging them to book the trip by providing partial payment option can help in increasing their confidence and ability to book the trip.\\r\\n\\r\\nCustomer may feel more comfortable to pay in installment. They can pay for a remaining portion of the payment in their own time. Partial payments can help you increase your conversion rate by reducing cart abandonment rates. By enabling the end user to have the ability to pay an installment, it increases interactions between the business owner and their customers.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe WP Travel Booking Partial Payment Plugin also helps site owner by sending reminder emails to customers of the due amount and provide them the ability to see their payment status in their dashboard. And when payment is completed, the end users are sent with a confirmation email. Such a transparent and seamless experience helps your business generate better business.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Why should you install this WordPress Booking Partial Payment Plugin on your Travel site?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>To Accept Partial Payment for Tour &amp; Trip Bookings<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add-on enables you to receive partial payment from your customer. The customer can pay for travel and tour package at the specified rate. You can set the installment rate and time for the trip while creating the package. So, the customer can choose the option of partial payment while checking out from a particular payment gateway. While they can pay for the remaining payment in installment basis. This feature provides flexibility in booking travel and tour package.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>To Send Automated Deposit Emails to end-users and admin<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add-on provides notification emails about the transaction. So, the customer can automatically track the amount that is left to be paid. When a purchase is made, the customer is notified about deposit amount and the remaining portion of the payment. And when the final amount is paid, email is sent to the customer about confirmation. It creates a smooth transition from one installment to another installment.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>For Clean Transaction Report<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nAll of the deposited payment made by the user is easily viewed in their respective tour booking dashboard. So, the customer can get the confirmation on every partial payment they made. The user can find details of the individual booking and details of the remaining amount from the dashboard. This feature helps the user and tour operator to make payment transparent and well informed. So, the user can be more confident about repeating the booking on your travel site.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>For Easy Integration With Your Travel Site<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis add-on gives you complete access to the settings of the partial payment options. You can easily integrate this add-on in your WordPress site. It does not require you to write complicated code to use this add-on. You can customize the add-on according to the user need. And it can be easily used with any payment gateway. So, it gives you the option to collect partial payment from any payment gateways.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/partial_payment_thumbnail.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 166,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 166,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"19.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 9263,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-khalti-checkout\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Khalti Checkout\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-02-27 05:39:57\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-08-02 08:45:22\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=9263\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-12699\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/wp-travel-khalti-checkout-banner.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1920\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">WP Travel Khalti Payment plugin is made for Nepali travel and tour websites built on WordPress to accept local payments in Nepali rupees. All transactions are done on a single page checkout. The process is instant, secure and hassle-free. It gives multiple payment options which include debit cards of various Nepali banks, Khalti wallet, and e-banking payment.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400\\\">Nepal has always been one of the best tourist de