     },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"19.99\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 10243,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-field-editor\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Field Editor\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-02-06 10:11:53\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-12-17 16:01:00\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=10243\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-13529 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/Banner.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"2910\\\" height=\\\"1162\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nWP Travel Field Editor add on provides the ability to add, edit, and remove a field in your travel package and itinerary pages while using the WP Travel plugin \\u2013 the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/\\\">best plugin for WordPress Travel websites<\\/a>. By installing this add on, you can boost your ability to add, edit and delete additional fields including fields for billing info, traveler info and trip inquiry form section making it easier for you to have as many fields as you want on the page.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhile this feature comes bundled in WP Travel Pro version, you will need to install this add on the free version of the plugin to have the ability to play around with fields. As a developer of a plugin and themes specially dedicated to travel agency websites on WordPress, we developed the Travel Field Editor add on to further boost your ability to do more on your travel website.\\r\\nThis add on makes your WP Travel plugin further customizable. You will have the ability to customize what field does and what doesn\\u2019t appear in your post and in what particular order. Here are some reasons why you should have it:\\r\\n<strong>Before You Proceed:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>The WP Travel Field editor requires the WP travel plugin to be installed, activated and configured.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Removing the core fields in your page may lead to the unexpected results sometimes.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>Core Features of WP Travel Field Editor:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Add a new custom field:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-13530\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/adding-new-field-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you want to add a new field in your travel form, easily do it by clicking on \\u201c+ Add file.\\u201d You can add custom fields in billing, traveler info and trip inquiry fields. The newly filled form contains options to provide values for Type, Name, Label, placeholder, validation and many more. With this fantastic user-oriented add on you can add new space for any information you want the user to fill in.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Edit field:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-13531 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/edit-the-field-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nWith field editor add-on you can edit the core and custom field in the billing, traveler info, and trip enquiry sections. You can have the option to provide new values for name, type. Label, text area validation, etc., in the edit form. This add-on is very much a handy tool when it comes to editing the form. Each form has its unique purpose to serve. You can edit the form by clicking the edit menu at the right.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Change field order:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-13532\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/04\\/change-field-order-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nThe add-on allows you to efficiently manage the display order of the checkout fields by using the drag and drop admin UI. Merely change the field order by moving fields up and down all you need to know is to move and click the mouse.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Remove field:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWell, you don\\u2019t need any fields on the form. No worries, you can go ahead and delete them straight away. Just click on the \\u201ccross\\u201d button at the right of the page.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Reset to factory setting:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nYes, you heard that right. This addon provides you the ability to reset your form fields to factory settings so that you can rebuild the form the way you want.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>How to Install the Addon?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nThe WP Travel Field editor only works with WP travel plugin. First, install and activate the WP Travel Plugin and integrate it with Field Editor. <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/documentations\\/wp-travel-field-editor\\/\\\">Click here<\\/a> to follow the installation tutorial.\\r\\n\\r\\nHave any questions, head on to our contact page and let us know your query. Always ready to help or want to some digging around, go on to our WP Field Editor forum pages.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/02\\/wp-travel-field-editor-logo.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2018,\n                        \"name\": \"Forms\",\n                        \"slug\": \"forms\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 2018,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 1,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 2017,\n                        \"nam