n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 8975,\n                \"slug\": \"wp-travel-wishlists\",\n                \"title\": \"WP Travel Wishlists\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-12-28 06:22:36\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-12-18 07:14:04\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/?post_type=download&p=8975\",\n                \"content\": \"<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-12302 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/wishlists-banner.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1920\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nIn regard to its features, the WP Travel Wishlist Plugin allows you to add a \\u201cWishlist\\u201d tab on the User Dashboard page on the user site.This is similar to bookmarking. It enables customers to create desired list of trips that they want to book and save them in their user account for future reference, thus improving the customer\\u2019s Traveling experience.\\r\\n\\r\\nWishlist is a simple but powerful tool that can help you to convert your site visitors into loyal customers. There are many situations when customers can\\u2019t book a trip at this time or simply don\\u2019t want. Possibility to bookmark the trips encourages users to return to your site and after all, make a trip booking.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Features of add-ons:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Add\\/Remove the wish list in user dashboard:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-12304 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/add-remove-the-wishlist-in-user-dashboard.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\nThis option allows you to either add or remove the trips in user dashboard. Adding is more like bookmarking your favorite trip to book it later and removing feature helps you to delete the trips if you don\'t like to book the trip.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Change the color of the icon:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-12305 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/change-color-of-the-icon.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nf you want to change the color of the wishlists icon then this option makes it possible to do so. You can change the color of the icon as per your requirement.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Change the wishlist icon:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-12306 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/change-add-to-wishlists-icon.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis option allows you change the icon for the wishlists. You can chose your preferred icon from the dropdown and save the settings.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Change the hover icon:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-12307 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/change-the-hover-text.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis option allows you to change the text that appears upon hovering wishlists icon.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Add the trips in wishlists from shortcode:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-12308 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/03\\/add-the-trips-in-wishlists-from-shortcode.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"880\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nThis plugin even allows to add the trips to the wishlist from the page where the trips are listed from shortcode.\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravel.io\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/wp-travel-wishlist-thumbnail.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n       